Package: ChestVolume
Title: Estimate the chest volumn with markers data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Wai Hang", "Kwong", , "wai-hang.kwong@polyu.edu.hk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1834-5715"))
Description: is an R package designed for analyzing chest expansion using 
3D marker coordinate data collected from motion capture systems. 
The package allows users to process marker data, adjust marker positions,
calculate convex hull volumes of chest segments, and visualize chest movements 
in both 2D and 3D.
